thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by James Irvine Kerr

author: James Irvine Kerr
title: James Irvine Kerr
text: After an initial hitch with vehicle availability at the time of booking we had excellent service from Omega. Prompt communication and friendly staff, and a clean well maintained vehicle to ensure we had a trouble free experience. Many thanks.
